  "summary": {
    "en": "A 120-piece fort building set for sturdier tents, secret bases, and collaborative indoor play.",
    "zh": "120件堡垒拼搭套装，适合更稳固的帐篷、秘密基地和多人室内互动。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 120-piece configuration provides more rods and connectors for taller, more stable house and tent structures.",
      "PP parts are lightweight, durable, and easy to assemble, store, and transport for home or retail use.",
      "Children can add fabric covers to turn the frame into a play tent, reading corner, or bedroom hideout.",
      "Custom colors, packaging, manuals, and branding can be discussed for OEM/ODM projects."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "120件配置提供更多杆件和连接球，可搭建更高、更稳定的房屋和帐篷结构。",
      "PP配件轻便耐用，便于家庭或零售场景中的组装、收纳和运输。",
      "儿童可在框架外添加布料，将其变成游戏帐篷、阅读角或卧室秘密基地。",
      "可根据OEM/ODM项目沟通颜色、包装、说明书和品牌定制。"
    ]
  },
